Package com.example.sumon.androidvolley

Class sendBoard

java.lang.Object
com.example.sumon.androidvolley.sendBoard
public class sendBoard extends Object
The sendBoard class represents a board object used in the Android application. It provides methods to retrieve, edit, and manipulate the board's grid, columns, and rows. This class is designed for managing a 3x3 grid of booleans to be send to another user in Multiplayer.
